@everyone We try not to overload this group with ZenMaid self-promotion; however, this episode of the Filthy Rich Cleaners podcast is probably one of the most important to-date in many ways.

So, even if you listen to 0 of the other episodes, I encourage anyone and everyone to give this one a listen where Stephanie Pipkin talks about safety and practical tips to keep your team (and yourself) safe. 

This one is a bit heavy, but well worth the listen!
